            "title": "ACWI: Healthy Rotation Among Global Stocks, Buy The Dip (Rating Upgrade)",
            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Group of young climate activists holding up a globe together by the sea\" data-id=\"1567445633\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1567445633/image_1567445633.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Alistair Berg</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>Global stocks have taken a hit since February 19. The same could be said five years ago when we were in the depths of the so-called COVID Crash. Back then, there were fears for not just financial markets, but indeed our</span></p>",
